See AGENTS.md — it is the canonical guidance file for AI agents (including Cursor) working in this repo.

Quick summary:
- Next.js 16 App Router + TypeScript + Tailwind v4 + shadcn/ui + Biome
- Better Auth (email OTP + TOTP) + Drizzle + Neon + Resend
- Server Components first; Zustand for UI only; Server Actions for mutations
- `proxy.ts` not `middleware.ts` (Next 16 naming)
- Do not add new dependencies without justifying in docs/tech-stack-decisions.md
- Commit convention: Conventional Commits

Read AGENTS.md before writing any code.
